+modal('jitera-desktop', "Jitera Desktop App")
  p During an intensive period of Context Next development, built a desktop application for Jitera as an exploratory side project.
  p The app provided a native interface to Jitera's agent capabilities, separate from the browser-based studio.
  p It was a welcome creative break during an otherwise incident-heavy sprint, and validated a product direction the team had been discussing for some time.
